👉 Questions are usually basic concept-based.

2️⃣ Important Economic Concepts
🔹 GDP (Gross Domestic Product)

Total value of goods & services produced in a country in a year.

🔹 Inflation

Increase in prices of goods and services.

🔹 Deflation

Decrease in price level.

🔹 Fiscal Policy

Government policy on taxation & spending.

🔹 Monetary Policy

Controlled by Reserve Bank of India (RBI).

3️⃣ Important Banking Facts

RBI established → 1935

Nationalization of banks → 1969

RBI controls monetary policy

